{
  "stem": "13238.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to leave everything in the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By then, they were coming already in our homes and taking out all the furniture, whatever they could put the hand on, because they knew exactly as we cannot touch anything.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was an ugly situation at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were terribly depressed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we were walking toward the ghetto, they were lining up the streets.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And was a ugly scene.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were throwing stones, spitting, and laughing, rejoicing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Stays with me till today.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Was a ugly scene.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lousy, bad.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Deprived of humanity.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Each and every one of us got from the committee a room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got two rooms, our family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But immediately after that, we got another family who were living in our house, and another couple.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were, together, 11 people staying in a room and a half.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A small kitchen, what [INAUDIBLE], yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was the same situation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're getting rations, like certain amount of bread or whatever was coming with it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was already very bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're most of the time hungry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was working in ghetto till 1942.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was a Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were actually controlling each and everybody's life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the superiors over them were Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were telling them exactly what they want.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were a number of times where they were expelling a few thousand Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So a list came in that the Judenrat sent the Jewish policeman to each and every house, bringing a [? contingence, ?] whatever they ask.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Like, from a family they could take one or two people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was going on for the first two years in ghetto-- from March 1941 till actually the liquidation of the ghetto, which was March 13, 1943.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There-- it was a hospital.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
